title: Patriots rolling, Cowboys and Chiefs showdown, Packers concerns with Vikings, Actor and Packers fan Brian Baumgartner in studio
itunes:title: Patriots rolling, Cowboys and Chiefs showdown, Packers concerns with Vikings, Actor and Packers fan Brian Baumgartner in studio
description:
In the latest edition of the Good Morning Football Podcast, hosts Kay Adams, Kyle Brandt, Peter Schrager and Nate Boyer examine the Patriots looking for a 5th straight win when they face the Falcons on Thursday Night Football. The Cowboys and Chiefs could be the matchup of the weekend, but has Kansas City returned to form? Kay answers Fantasy Football questions before Actor Brian Baumgartner joins the show to discuss his beloved Packers, biggest comeback players and his new book on the 'The Office'.

The Good Morning Football Podcast is part of the NFL Podcast Network.
